Package domain

Class Packaging

java.lang.Object
domain.Packaging
All Implemented Interfaces:
DomainObject, Serializable
public class Packaging extends Object implements DomainObject
Klasa koja predstavlja nacin pakovanja sladoleda. Klasa implementira interfejs DomainObject. Pakovanje ima svoj id i naziv pakovanja.

Vanja Jankovic
